TIMERS
\layout Standard

Represent count down timers! 
\layout Standard

Timers have 4 contacts.
 
\layout Itemize

E-for enable (input) 
\layout Itemize

D-for done (output) 
\layout Itemize

C -for continue 
\layout Itemize

R-for running (output) - 
\layout Itemize

E (input) -enable -will start the timer when true.
 
\layout Standard

The timer count resets when the E input goes false.
 
\layout Standard

R (output) -running -will be true will the count is running.
\layout Standard

C (input) -continue -is not used in EMC for legacy reasons so is always
 forced true.
 
